;" />，可得<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004953986609.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" /><br />（2）设此时封闭气体压强为<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954220352.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，封闭气体的长度<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954236609.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，根据理想气体状态方程可得<br /><img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954251845.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />计算可得<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954267744.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" /><br />此时作用液面高度差<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954282857.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" /><br />左端液面上升<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954298688.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，右端上升<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954329887.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，所以开口端注入水银的长度为<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140825/20140825004954345676.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" /></div></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
